{"tid":2147814,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實咁多香港人同台灣人玩傳說對決 仲講咩抵制騰訊？","createTime":"2020-08-09T13:19:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T13:24:39.000Z","uid":91914,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"de583029b69c2f085d5b8f1643acc732da6028ee","tid":2147814,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T13:19:09.000Z","msg":"除咗香港台灣之外，係日韓泰都十分受歡迎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望咁多位仲有玩既連登仔即刻del game <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《傳說對決》（英語：Arena of Valor，簡稱傳說）是一款5v5多人線上戰鬥技術型遊戲。是Garena 與<span class=\"red\">天美工作室</span>群共同開發，於2016年10月1日起在Android平台進行封閉測試[1][2]，並於兩週後正式上市，開放下載[3][4]。2017年7月啟動GCS職業聯賽[5]。2018年宣佈成為2018年亞洲運動會電子競技比賽六款遊戲其中之一<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">天美工作室群是騰訊遊戲旗下的遊戲工作室</span>，工作室群下設天美J1、天美J2、天美J3、天美J4、天美J5、天美J6、天美T1、天美L1八個工作室。2014年10月9日，騰訊互動娛樂自研遊戲組織體系進行調整，將琳琅天上、天美藝游、臥龍工作室合併成天美工作室群[1]"},{"pid":"50e3cac9e382b9ffb9842771baa1d6ea56441378","tid":2147814,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T13:21:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5a41527d7a030c113b87d1d1d2a8f868696d800","tid":2147814,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T13:21:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96d3bd4bd71e4ef5e13b1c7d9ce28f59190a5d94","tid":2147814,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T13:24:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}